_text = "I’m waiting in the line. If you don’t have a reservation, good luck getting onto the ferry.\n\nI've spent two separate vacations sleeping overnight in this line up. Both times I slept in the driver seat, fearing that I wouldn't wake up in time for the first ferry. Spoiler alert, I was up at 5am and made both of them.Was I well rested? No, but it was worth it.\n\nThere's something exciting about sleeping in a car, waiting for your next voyage. The call for adventure is just electrifying.I hope I get to return this summer.\n\nMy memory of this place ends here"

//this is only for left or right choice
roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MemoryTunnelRoom3, MemoryTunnelRoom3, false)

